dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Mariposa Peak quadrangle, Merced, San Benito and Santa Clara counties, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Mariposa Peak, CA 1969, photoinspected 1978, DMA 1757 I NW -- series V895." "First printing, July 2007." Includes location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology, most recent 1999. Includes "pertinent references", most recent 1975.
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
